				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/interview" rel="tag">interview</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/leap" rel="tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/london-real-tv" rel="tag">London Real TV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/open-source-2" rel="tag">open source</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/prohibition" rel="tag">prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/snowden" rel="tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war-on-drugs" rel="tag">war on drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
					</footer><!-- #entry-meta -->
	</article><!-- #post-3382 -->

				
					
	<article id="post-3375" class="post-3375 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-acta category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-gchq category-intelligence category-interviews category-isc category-law category-leap category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-nsa category-osa category-politics category-privacy-2 category-prohibition-2 category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-syria category-terrorism category-tv category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-gchq tag-intelligence-2 tag-internet tag-interview tag-isc tag-leap tag-london-real-tv tag-national-security-2 tag-nsa tag-oversight tag-privacy tag-prohibition tag-security tag-snowden tag-surveillance-2 tag-terrorism-2 tag-war-on-drugs tag-whistleblowers-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/london-real-tv-interview-coming-soon.html" title="Permalink to London Real TV Interview — coming soon" rel="bookmark">London Real <span class="caps">TV</span> Interview — coming soon</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/london-real-tv-interview-coming-soon.html" title="13:00" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-10-12T13:00:23+00:00" pubdate>October 12, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/10/london-real-tv-interview-coming-soon.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is a taster of my recent inter­view on <a href="http://www.londonreal.tv/">Lon­don Real <span class="caps">TV</span></a>. It was diverse, lively and fun, and should be broad­cast in full tomor­row:<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/76652647" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/76652647">Annie Machon — Whis­tleblower — Lon­don Real <span class="caps">TV</span></a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
