	<article id="post-2594" class="post-2594 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-gaddafi category-injunctions category-intelligence category-ip category-law category-leap category-media category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-osa category-politics category-spies category-surveillance category-talks-2 category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-iceland tag-icij tag-intelligence-2 tag-journalism tag-kristinn-hrafnsson tag-law-2 tag-leap tag-media-2 tag-mi5 tag-mi6 tag-prohibition tag-snarrotin tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2 tag-talks tag-war tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/talk-at-the-icelandic-centre-for-investigative-journalism.html" title="Permalink to Talk at the Icelandic Centre for Investigative Journalism" rel="bookmark">Talk at the Icelandic Centre for Investigative Journalism</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/talk-at-the-icelandic-centre-for-investigative-journalism.html" title="19:49" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-02-21T19:49:01+00:00" pubdate>February 21, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/talk-at-the-icelandic-centre-for-investigative-journalism.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Wikileaks spokes­man, Kris­tinn Hrafns­son, invited me to speak at the <a href="http://www.icij.is/?page_id=23">Icelandic Centre for Invest­ig­at­ive Journ­al­ism</a> while I was in Ice­land in February.</p>
<p>While focus­ing on the inter­sec­tion and con­trol between intel­li­gence and the media, my talk also explores many of my other cur­rent areas of interest.<br />
<iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/61673862" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/61673862">Ice­land Journ­al­ists talk 2013</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="http://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
