	<article id="post-2236" class="post-2236 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-drugs-2 category-interviews category-leap category-mi5 category-prohibition-2 category-radio category-spies category-whistleblowers tag-czech-republic tag-leap tag-legalisation tag-mi5 tag-prohibition tag-spies-2 tag-war-on-drugs tag-whistleblowing">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/interview-czech-national-radio.html" title="Permalink to Interview, Czech National Radio" rel="bookmark">Interview, Czech National Radio</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/interview-czech-national-radio.html" title="18:31" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-12-22T18:31:44+00:00" pubdate>December 22, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/interview-czech-national-radio.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is a link to an <a href="https://soundcloud.com/anniemachon/prague-national-radio-november">in-depth inter­view</a> I did recently at the <a href="http://www.radiocesko.cz/">Czech national radio sta­tion</a> in Prague.</p>
<p>As a Dir­ector of Law Enforce­ment Against Pro­hib­i­tion (<a href="http://www.leap.cc/"><span class="caps">LEAP</span></a>), I was invited to Prague by the pro­gress­ive Czech National Drug Co-ordinator, Jindrich Voboril, to speak at a drugs con­fer­ence in the Czech Par­lia­ment.<br />
<iframe src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Ftracks%2F81637347" height="166" width="100%" frameborder="no" scrolling="no"></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/interview-czech-national-radio.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/interviews" title="View all posts in Interviews" rel="category tag">Interviews</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/leap" title="View all posts in LEAP" rel="category tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi5" title="View all posts in MI5" rel="category tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/prohibition-2" title="View all posts in Prohibition" rel="category tag">Prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/radio" title="View all posts in Radio" rel="category tag">Radio</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
