	<article id="post-3409" class="post-3409 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-afghanistan category-drugs-2 category-economics category-law category-leap category-police category-politics category-prohibition-2 category-talks-2 category-terrorism tag-drugs tag-economics-2 tag-law-2 tag-leap tag-police-2 tag-prohibition tag-release tag-terrorism-2 tag-the-house-i-live-in tag-the-war-on-drugs tag-transform">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/house-live-drug-panel-discussion.html" title="Permalink to “The House I Live In” — drug panel discussion" rel="bookmark"><span class="dquo">“</span>The House I Live In” — drug panel discussion</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/house-live-drug-panel-discussion.html" title="19:38" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-12-18T19:38:45+00:00" pubdate>December 18, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/house-live-drug-panel-discussion.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>I recently rep­res­en­ted <a href="http://www.leap.cc/"><span class="caps">LEAP</span></a> at a panel dis­cus­sion in Lon­don about the failed war on drugs after a screen­ing of the excel­lent film <em>The House I Live In</em>, along with Steve Rolles of <a href="http://www.tdpf.org.uk/">Trans­form</a> and Niamh East­wood of <a href="http://www.release.org.uk/">Release</a>:<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/59218640" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/59218640">Oval Space Cinema Club: ‘The House I Live In’ — Panel Dis­cus­sion</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/ovalspace">Oval Space</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/12/house-live-drug-panel-discussion.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/afghanistan" title="View all posts in Afghanistan" rel="category tag">Afghanistan</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/economics" title="View all posts in Economics" rel="category tag">Economics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/leap" title="View all posts in LEAP" rel="category tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/prohibition-2" title="View all posts in Prohibition" rel="category tag">Prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/talks-2" title="View all posts in Talks" rel="category tag">Talks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>			</span>
